/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13104920/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13104920/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13104920/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13104920/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13104920/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13104920/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13104920/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13104920/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13104920/scor-4060-enduro-trail-mtb-frame-storage-sram-udh-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>On the underside of the downtube you’ll notice some frame storage; tucked away in there is a spare SRAM UDH hanger, leaving enough room for a multitool and some tire plugs too. Mounting points on the downtube provide dedicated mounting for accessories, as well as your water bottle.</p><h3>SCOR 4060 Z</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor.jpg\" alt=\"scor 4060 z emtb shimano ep8 motor 720 wh battery\" width=\"1600\" height=\"907\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-297x168.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-800x454.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-768x435.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-1536x871.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-297x168.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-800x454.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-768x435.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13105741/scor-4060-z-emtb-shimano-ep8-motor-1536x871.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>The SCOR 4060 Z is the eMTB version, with the exact same geometry as the SCOR 4060. It retains the ability to switch between 140mm and 160mm travel configurations, but houses a Shimano EP8 motor, capable of an 85 Nm output, paired with a Shimano-approved 720 Wh battery.&nbsp;</p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p>The SCOR 4060 is available either as an enduro bike with 160mm rear travel, the 4060 LT, or as a trail bike with 140mm rear travel, the 4060 ST. Both bikes are available in two spec options with the top-of-the-line models selling for €6299 and the base model for €4299. There are also framesets available for €3499 (LT) or €3299 (ST).</p><p>The top-of-the-line SCOR 4060 Z eMTB retails at €8299 and the base model at €6299. The first lot of 4060 complete bikes and framesets are available now with 4060 Z stock due in October 2021.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.scor-mtb.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>SCOR-MTB.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"c9978d6377c1579ea6e9223fbda540b1fb50ebb54ee0ec1e80774e827f9e3edb","category":"Cycling"}